sorcer.core.context.model

Interface Variability<T>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Evaluation<T>, Identifiable, Perturbation<T>, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Agent, Par, ParImpl

    public interface Variability<T>
extends Identifiable, Evaluation<T>, Perturbation<T>, Serializable
    A variable has id, name and value. Its value can be evaluated by a related Evaluator.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  Variability.MathType 
      static class  Variability.Type
      Types allow for grouping in the functional model so all variables of a particular type can be retrieved as a functional collection, e.g., DESIGN, RESPONSE, DERIVATIVE or GRADIENT.
